Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.50,0:00:07.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:11.37,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Yeah... But still, there are just too many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.37,0:00:14.08,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.08,0:00:17.71,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Seems like you're having trouble, Fullmetal!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.82,0:00:23.82,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Battle requires efficiency.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.82,0:00:30.89,Helvetica,,0,0,3,,{\fs22}If you face an enemy overwhelming you with numbers one-on-one,\Nyou’ll eventually wear yourself out and collapse.
