Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.99,0:00:33.16,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.16,0:00:37.40,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,And battle also requires beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.37,0:00:44.01,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Lord Armstrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.01,0:00:50.21,Helvetica,,0,0,3,,{\fs22}Beautiful physiques hold beautiful techniques;\Nbeautiful techniques hold beautiful power!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.21,0:00:56.22,Helvetica,,0,0,3,,{\fs22}Behold, the artistic alchemy passed down through generations of the Armstrong family!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:00:57.75,Helvetica,,0,0,3,,{\fs22\move(256,445,256,493)}Behold, the artistic alchemy passed down through generations of the Armstrong family!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.75,0:01:02.36,Helvetica,,0,0,3,,{\fs22}Enough with the boring lecture.\NJust get to the point, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.86,0:01:07.30,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Wait, hold on a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.06,0:01:12.83,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Did you already... figure it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.07,0:01:20.18,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,{\fs25}We have a problem, Edward! Armony has been kidnapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:22.95,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,What?! Armony? By whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:26.62,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,{\fs25}Greta, the assistant. She’s probably still inside the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.62,0:01:31.12,Helvetica,,0,0,3,,{\fs22}Leave this to us. Go after her!\NShe's surely waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.12,0:01:32.12,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.12,0:01:33.51,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.51,0:01:35.49,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
